&lt;h1 id="ancient-grace"&gt;ANCIENT GRACE&lt;/h1&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I revere old, simple ways of doing things. As our mad “economic” drive for growth winds down, and the world discards the quest for profits for the rich few, we’ll find that we have time again for a lot that has fallen by the wayside in the past century of more.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.hanglipcore.net/2020\03\beyond-grace.html?utm_source=all&amp;amp;utm_medium=Atom"&gt;&lt;em&gt;More&amp;hellip;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</content></entry>
