&lt;h4 id="we-have-a-year"&gt;WE HAVE A YEAR&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We have a year or two: so, to be purposeful let&amp;rsquo;s say 1 year. Starting on the 1st of March 2020, we want to restore old crop lands, consistent with the notion of Farm Within a Farm, or Core Farm.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.hanglipcore.net/2020\02\from-march-1-2020.html?utm_source=all&amp;amp;utm_medium=Atom"&gt;&lt;em&gt;More&amp;hellip;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</content></entry>
